author: makortel
body:
#### PR description:

Dictionary for `AbsHcalAlgoData` is required to get the version and checksum of HFPhase1PMTParams. I also cleaned up `classes.h`. Found with https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/45423#issuecomment-2226416814

Resolves https://github.com/cms-sw/framework-team/issues/963

#### PR validation:

Code compiles, and the to-be-added `edmDumpClassVersion` succeeds to process the `classes_def.xml` files.
title: Add dictionary for AbsHcalAlgoData
